
<div class="web-title-phrase">
    <div class="text-web-title-phrase">
        <h1 class="title">PetGossip</h1>
        <p class="phrase">Whether it's a question about their health, behavior, or simply showcasing their cuteness, Gossip Pets is the go-to platform.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="web-description">
    <div class="img-web-description">
        
    </div>
    <div class="description-info">
        <div class="description-info-text">
            <h2>WHAT IS PET GOSSIP?</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Gossip Pets, the online hub where your furry, feathery, or scaly friends take the spotlight! 
                Here, it's all about your pet - their quirks, health concerns, and the adorable chaos they bring into your life. 
                <br>
                <br>
                Create personalized profiles for your beloved companions and connect with a passionate pet community. Share your experiences, seek advice, and celebrate the uniqueness of your pet pals. 
                <br>
                <br>
                Whether it's a question about their health, behavior, or simply showcasing their cuteness, Gossip Pets is the go-to platform.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="web-description-extra-info">
            <a href="/info"><button class="btn-web-description-extra-info">Learn more about our community</button></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br><br>
<div class="profilesPet">
    <div class="profilesPet-container profilesPet-view-all">
        <a href="/view-all-pets">
            <div class="profilesPet-img view-all-shape">
                <p class="view-all-shape-text">View All Pets</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    {{#each foundPets}}
        <div class="profilesPet-container">
            <img class="profilesPet-img" src="{{img}}" alt="Pet's img">
            <p class="profilesPet-name">{{name}}</p>
        </div>
    {{/each}}
</div>
<br><br>

